name: Macroblock Tree
description:
This composition is part of a triptych with OBJKT#270354 and OBJKT#192686.
They were exhibited at the graduating show from "La Cambre" Kanal Centre Pompidou in Brussels in 2019.

They have a particular place in my collection of Abstract Glitch Compositions because they are less RAW than the others and represent the top of my experimentations during these years of research.
